    dc:description "Figure 8. Galumna granulimorpha sp. nov. (A) Dorsal view of idiosoma; (B) dorsofrontal view of prodorsum, partial; (C) lateral view of sensillus; (D) ventral view of idiosoma; (E) posterior view of opisthonotum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4006691/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4006693>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Morphological characters of different species. (A–D) Galumna granulimorpha sp. nov. (A) Rostrum (arrow indicates central carina); (B) lateral view of sensillus; (C) pteromorph; (D) porose areas A3 and Ap. (E–H) Pergalumna iunctiporosa sp. nov. (E) Rostrum (arrow indicates central carina); (F) pteromorph; (G) porose areas, lyrifussure and opisthonotal gland opening; (H) dorsolateral view of sensillus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4006693/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

